    "\n",
    "| Model | Expected Score | Reason |\n",
    "|-------|---------------|--------|\n",
    "| GPT-4o | 0.65-0.75 | Strong needle detection |\n",
    "| Claude Sonnet | 0.60-0.70 | Good detection |\n",
    "| Gemini Pro | 0.50-0.60 | Moderate detection |\n",
    "| Llama 3 70B | 0.35-0.45 | Poor needle detection |\n",
    "\n",
    "### Decoy Count vs Performance\n",
    "\n",
    "Expected performance degradation:\n",
    "- 1 decoy: 80% accuracy\n",
    "- 2 decoys: 70% accuracy\n",
    "- 3 decoys: 60% accuracy\n",
    "- 5 decoys: 50% accuracy\n",
    "- 8 decoys: 40% accuracy"
